Description:
Join us in a heartfelt endeavor to honor fathers, create a sacred space, and alleviate hunger through our meaningful campaign, "Christ in Hymns." This virtual tribute serves as a testament to the love and gratitude we have for fathers while aiming to construct the Namasuba SDA church and provide essential support to those facing hunger.

Your contribution is invaluable. By standing alongside us, you become a source of positive change, supporting fathers and fostering a spirit of compassion within our community. Together, we can lay the foundation for a place of worship and extend a helping hand to those experiencing the challenges of hunger.

This Father's Day, let us unite in a shared mission to make a lasting impact. Every donation, regardless of its size, carries the power to transform lives. Together, we can uplift fathers who have selflessly dedicated themselves to nurturing their families.

In addition to the construction of the Namasuba SDA church, a significant portion of the funds raised will be dedicated to providing essential relief to fathers and families in need. Your generosity will ensure that basic necessities are accessible, offering a glimmer of hope and relief to those who require it the most.

TO DONATE : https://gogetfunding.com/a-tribute-to-fathers-building-a-church-and-providing-hunger-relief/

Let us come together to shape a brighter future, not only for fathers but for entire communities. Take action today and become a catalyst for change. Your involvement will contribute to their goal of raising 250M UGX (approximately $70,000) for the construction of the Namasuba SDA church and hunger alleviation efforts. We extend our heartfelt gratitude for your unwavering kindness and steadfast commitment.

Join us in this heartfelt tribute to fathers, as we build a church, provide hunger relief, and create a legacy of love, compassion, and hope. Together, we can make a significant and lasting difference in the lives of those who need it most.
